    "title_romaji": "Legend of the Galactic Heroes",
    "title_native": "銀河英雄伝説",
    "synopsis": "<p>For decades, the Galactic Empire has been locked in an interstellar war with the Free Planets Alliance, a conflict that involves thousands of spaceships and millions of soldiers on both sides. Two new commanders enter the conflict with great hopes: Imperial Admiral Reinhard von Lohengramm and the FPA's Yang Wen-Li. As they deal with superiors and subordinates, maneuver through complicated political arrangements, plot strategies, and win battles, each will be tested, and ultimately, changed, by the reality of war.<br><span class=\"media-description-source\">&nbsp;&nbsp;—&nbsp;Source: Anime News Network</span></p>",
